---
title: Smart Double Salmon and Lemony Lentil Bowls with Garlicky Feta Crema
description: Seared salmon fillets get a flavour boost from garlicky feta cheese sauce, all sitting atop a bed of lemony lentils, roasted sweet potatoes and ever-so-slightly wilted baby spinach. Eat until your heart's content with this carb and cal-conscious bowl.

